text: Phoebe Ebimiekumo (born 17 January 1974) is a Nigerian former footballer defender. Ebimiekumo played for the Nigeria women's national football team. She played for her team in the 1991 FIFA Women's World Cup and the 1995 FIFA Women's World Cup. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:1995 FIFA Women's World Cup players Category:Association football defenders Category:1991 FIFA Women's World Cup players
